"Kumoni" is a fluffy cloud fairy (cloud + demon combined) and he can be anything! *Cloud is called “Kumo” and Daemon is called “Oni” in Japanese. (Kumoni=Kumo+Oni) The concept for Kumoni is “clouds are equivalent that anyone in the world can see.” Kumoni is trying his best to become popular!!! ※"Kumoni" series artwork cannot be used for commercial purposes, but can be used for personal use, such as setting Kumoni as an icon for social networking sites or printing it out and displaying it on the wall of a room.
